snippet.title: GunSuit Guardians - EARLY ACCESS available NOW!
snippet.description:
EARLY ACCESS available NOW ➡ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2278830/GunSuit_Guardians/

Gear up your GunSuit and defend Earth from an alien siege! Equip and upgrade unique arsenals of overpowered weapons to survive overwhelming numbers in this action-roguelite twin-stick horde survival.

⭐ Mailing List: http://eepurl.com/gv2FRT
⭐ Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/mattglanville
⭐ Discord: https://discord.gg/zCyJuy8
⭐ itch.io: https://crowbarska.itch.io/
